OL,3,CHarry Styles to perform at the Brit
OL,4,CAwards
OL,6,FHarry Styles has been announced as the
OL,7,Flatest artist set to perform at the
OL,8,FBrit Awards 2026.
OL,10,FThe former One Direction singer is
OL,11,Fcurrently preparing to release his
OL,12,Ffourth album, as well as embark on a
OL,13,Fseries of arena and stadium
OL,14,Fresidencies around the world.
OL,16,FHarry, 31, will perform at the awards
OL,17,Fat the Co-Op Live Arena in Manchester
OL,18,Fon Saturday, 28 February - the first
OL,19,Ftime since his last world tour
OL,20,Fconcluded in July 2023.
