OL,3,CHarry Styles to perform at the Brit
OL,4,CAwards
OL,6,FIt is the first time in history that
OL,7,Fthe event is being held outside of
OL,8,FLondon.
OL,10,FHarry Styles' performance will be the
OL,11,Ffirst live TV performance debut of
OL,12,Fmusic from his new album.
OL,14,FThe first single taken from that
OL,15,Falbum, Aperture, was released last
OL,16,Fweek as well as news of a seven city
OL,17,Fresidency, comprising 50 dates across
OL,18,FAmsterdam, London, Sao Paulo, Mexico
OL,19,FCity, New York, Melbourne, and Sydney,
OL,20,Fincluding a record-breaking 12-night
OL,21,Frun at London's Wembley Stadium.
