OL,4,CAwards
OL,6,FStyles is the second performer
OL,7,Fannounced for the 2026 show, joining
OL,8,FOlivia Dean who has five nominations.
OL,10,FLola Young is also nominated five
OL,11,Ftimes, closely followed by Sam Fender
OL,12,Fwith four nominations for his album
OL,13,F'People Watching', following his
OL,14,FMercury Prize win last year.
