OL,3,CHarry Styles to perform at the Brit
OL,4,CAwards
OL,6,FBritpop band Pulp scored their first
OL,7,Fnomination since since 1996, while
OL,8,FLily Allen was nominated in three
OL,9,Fcategories after her West End Girl
OL,10,Falbum caused a stir detailing the
OL,11,Falleged infidelity of her ex-husband
OL,12,FDavid Harbour.
OL,14,FStyles previously performed at the
OL,15,FBrit awards in 2023, which saw him
OL,16,Ftake home four awards for his album
OL,17,F"Harry's House".
