OL,3,CHarry Styles to perform at the Brit
OL,4,CAwards
OL,6,FHarry's House was his third studio
OL,7,Falbum, following the release of his
OL,8,Fself titled debut album in 2017 and
OL,9,Fhis second - Fine Line - in 2019,
OL,10,Fwhich reached number one and number
OL,11,Ftwo one the UK Albums Chart
OL,12,Frespectively.
OL,14,FStyles' performance will be broadcast
OL,15,Flive from Manchester on 28 February on
OL,16,FITV, ahead of the release of his
OL,17,Fhighly anticipated fourth album: Kiss
OL,18,FAll The Time, Disco Occasionally in
OL,19,FMarch.
